content.text: Let me help you start Firefox to do some testing. First, I'll take a screenshot to see the desktop, then click on Firefox.
I see the Firefox icon on the desktop. Let me click on it to open the browser.

Firefox has opened successfully. Following our instructions, I'll ignore the startup wizard and directly click on the address bar to start browsing. Let me know what specific website or search term you'd like me to enter.
I've clicked on the address bar and it's ready for input. What website would you like me to visit?
